criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject is above 20 years of age;

          -  Subject is indicated for A-SPINE Spinal Fixation System;

          -  Subject is willing and able to provide informed consent to participate in the study;

          -  Subject is willing and able to understand the purpose of the study, his/her role, and
             is available to return to the clinic/hospital for all required follow-up visits.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects will be excluded if, in the opinion of the Investigator, the subject does not
             qualify based on approved labeling requirements or Subject Inclusion Criteria.
